{
  "text": "1 See e.g. Mash 1993, 204-210; [CITATION_1] , 12-13, Dowd 2015 , 56, Traphagan 2015 and Darling 2016, s.vv. 'atomism,' 'Leucippus,' 'Democritus,' 'Metrodorus,' 'Epicurus' and 'Lucretius.' 2 See e.g. Lucretius 6.649-652. Henceforth all references to Lucretius will follow the text and translation of Rouse and Smith 1992, unless otherwise specified. 3 For the Presocratic antecedents of these arguments see Furley 1989, 110-114; [CITATION_2] Asmis 1984, 261-267. ",
